Question: Describe what you did last weekend.
Answer:
last weekend i went shopping with my students to the outlet. we were supposed to be there by two, but one of the girl, S, was running late so we ended up meeting at 3:30. by that time, all of us finally met each other and some of them met for the first time. it was a very warm and welcoming atmosphere. though it was really brief, everyone bounded immediately. 
then Nick, Sarina and I went on shopping. Sarina, despite all her savings trouble, bought a kate spade purse for herself as a birthday gift. and then i got myself two new dresses and a t-shirt. because Sarina had spent all her money on the purse, i got to buy a nice top for her as a birthday gift. and both of us were happy with the result.
finally we went to the chocolate factory and ate a big piece of cheese cake dipped into dark chocolate. but it was really tasty despite the fact it was too fattening.
what a productive weekend!